    <entry>
      <title>Rancher容器平台搭建</title>
      <link href="/post/4f5f6025.html"/>
      <url>/post/4f5f6025.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="单节点Rancher安装"><a href="#单节点Rancher安装" class="headerlink" title="单节点Rancher安装"></a>单节点Rancher安装</h2><blockquote><p>适用于对可视化面板的可用性要求不高的环境，生产环境基本也够用了。</p><p>只需要注意对Rancher的存储目录 <code>/var/lib/rancher</code> 进行定期备份即可。</p><p>以下的单节点部署过程中需要占用8443端口，可以根据部署环境自行调整。</p></blockquote><ul><li>部署</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用Rancher生成的默认自签名证书</span></span><br><span class="line">docker run -d --restart=unless-stopped \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 8443:443 \</span><br><span class="line">  --privileged \</span><br><span class="line">  -v /var/lib/rancher:/var/lib/rancher \</span><br><span class="line">  rancher/rancher:latest</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果需要使用自己的证书可以参考以下链接</span></span><br><span class="line">https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/zh/v2.6/pages-for-subheaders/rancher-on-a-single-node-with-docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
